<span class="inline-flex items-center bg-green-100 text-green-800 text-base font-medium mr-2 px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded-full">
  <span class="w-2 h-2 mr-1 bg-green-500 rounded-full"></span>
  Оновлення
</span>
